      <title>日本储户藏有四万亿日元。这是多少钱</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-21/japanese-savers-have-a-quadrillion-yen-stashed-away-here-s-how-much-that-is</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着日本股市在经历了数十年的低迷之后飙升至历史新高，政府现在正试图鼓励散户投资者将其 1000 亿日元的现金储蓄投入股市。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-21/japanese-savers-have-a-quadrillion-yen-stashed-away-here-s-how-much-that-is</guid>
